    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Biome: Deserts</em></p>\\n<p>Growing close to the ground in arid areas, this plant produces three wide, thick leaves that spread outward to capture moisture and shade the soil. Its deep roots seek hidden reservoirs below the sand. Nicknamed the “bread of the desert,” the plant develops large spherical fruits nearly the size of a man’s head. The fruits have a tough, leathery rind but a soft, cake-like interior; each contains enough nutrients to sustain four people for a day. Farming Balon’s Plant is difficult: the seeds only mature when deposited within a medium creature at death, where decomposition gases trigger rapid seed development and feed the young plant’s root system.</p>",
